a Approved on 3rd nomination October 2023. Disapproved on 2 previous nominations: September 2009 and February 2023. Recommendation for infantile KD, as defined by low GALC enzyme and psychosine ≥ 10 nM, forwarded to SHHS on 1 March 2024. b Approved on 3rd nomination. Not approved June 2016 and November 2016.
